text: Cicatrisestola humeralis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Martins and Galileo in 1995. It is known from Argentina and Bolivia.BioLib.cz - Cicatrisestola humeralis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1995
